Prerequisites:
•	7 Servers (3 controller+storage, 3 compute+storage, 1 Deployment server)
•	Linux servers running Ubuntu 24.04 LTS
•	Minimum 3 Interfaces
•	Internet Connection
•	Ceph version Squid
•	OpenStack version 2024.2
•	Python Version 3.9 & above
•	All Storage nodes should have additional unmounted drive to be managed by Ceph

